theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Incoming Transmission from Pulsar...>


Do I need to make myself any clearer!?

HURRY UP!


I'm detecting massive energy pulses coming from down below the central tower of this station. 

To direct enough energy to destroy a star the ancients used the 8 massive spires as a focusing lense.

Fortunately, the ancients had the wise idea to include a manual override for each spire.

At the base of the towers, in the pit below, are four buttons that you can use to deactivate the spires. 

There's also four more for the spires of the central tower. 


It's not a permanent solution, but it prevents the Nexyr from activating the Void Bringer right now.

Maybe, without anywhere to go, the energy will build and build until it destroys itself.

We can only hope. 

But for now,



Deactivate the spires, save the world.



<End Transmission>"

