bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Incoming Transmission From Grandmaster J'yma>

<Translating...>

Understand, Pulsar, that you have not won.

Yes, I know your name, AI.


Earth will BURN.

Yes, we know your home planet, human.

I will bring the entire might of the Nexyr Empire and RAZE your home fleet, destroy every city, and glass the surface of your world until there is NOTHING LEFT.



This is not over. 


You have embarrased me before the Emperor and ruined our greatest hope.


You have only temporarily halted our march to victory.


Control of the universe will be ours.





<End transmission>"

