[node name="Label" type="RichTextLabel" parent="TerminalPage3/MarginContainer" unique_id=403958640]
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0, 1, 0, 1)
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("2_ntxbk")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Incoming Transmission from Pulsar...>

You're right, Grandmaster J'yma, this is not over. 


We're just getting started.


How about I take your ship for my own, and make your crew drink vacuum, as a warmup?



Oh, you're still here.


I suppose I should thank you, <the Champi}>, t/2 Hero, th\" Vict,r>

I will notify Earth that the White Winged Guardian is coming home, although you and the ship will probably get there first.

As for me? I have unfinished buisness here. Deactivating the spires actually destroyed the Void Bringer, by the way. The energy overloaded the core of the tower, and it detonated milliseconds after I teleported you out.

Did you ever wonder what the source of the signal was? The one that brought us here, right when we were needed.

It was you.

I cannot explain this. Perhaps we will know sometime in the future.

If our paths meet again, then I await that day.

If not, then goodbye. Don't worry about the Nexyr. I'll deal with them. Permanently.


<End Transmission>"

